quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  2,154,"Wata on wi'u-onon muumini en-fii …ďen waretee…ďe e laawol Allah:"Ko maayir…ďe wano fof maayirta".Ko woni,…ďen ko wuur…ďe ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe, kono on so'ataa nguurdam ma…ď…ďe;sa…ďu ko …óam nguurdam heerii-…óam, …óam anndortaako si wanaa wahyu immor…óo ka Allah."
  2,155,"Ma Men jariba on nooneeji e musiibaaji; wano hulugol ay…ďe mo'on, e heege sabu Ňčakkireede √Īaametee, e …óoytagol jawle …óen sabu waaseede …óen maa sa…ótugol he…óde …óe, e …óuytoral woŇčkiiji …óin sabu boneeji halkay…ói yim…ďe …ďen, maa yanirgol shahiidi fii Allah, e …óuytoral dim…óe leydi ndin, wewlin -an nulaa…óo- …ďen mu√Ī√Īotoo…ďe …óin musiibaaji sabu ko O Eltani…ďe aduna e laaxara."
  2,156,"∆Āen taw…ďe si gootel e …óin musiibaaji he…ďii…ďe,…ďe wi'ira yarluyee e jebbilaare:Menen ko men jeyaa…ďe Allah,Himo Wa…óa e amen kon ko O muuyi,ko ka Makko kadi woni ruttorde amen √Īalnde darngal,ko Kanko Woni Tag…óo men,O Teddiniri men neemaaji seertu…ói, ko ka Makko woni ruttorde amen e lannoode fiyaaku amen."
  2,157,"Ena woodani …ďen sifor…ďe …óii sifaaji,maŇčtoore immorde ka Allah,ndeer mbatu malaa'ika en toowungu,e yurmeende jippotoonde e ma…ď…ďe.Ko …ďee …óoo ngoni feewir…ďe laawol goonga ngol."
  2,158,"Pelle Safaa e Marwa …óen takko ka suudu Kaaba, ko jeyaa…óe e maandeeji shari'a …ďaŇčngu…óo on. Kala on faandii…óo suudu Kaaba ndun fii tottugol dewal hajju maa umara, ella woo fawaaki mo nde o wanngotoo hakkunde majji; tawa himo fi…ďi …óum ko fiyaaku majjiyaŇčkoo…ďe jeyaa, gom…óii non Allah ∆ĀaŇčnginii wonde …óum ko e dewe hajju jeyaa. Kala on huuwu…óo yi…óaa…ói …óin ka dewe hara himo la…ď…ďini; pellet Allah Jaarnay mo, O Ja…ďana mo …óum, O Yo…ďa mo; tawde KaŇčko Allah Ko O Anndu…óo …ďen huuway…ďe mo∆ī∆īere, haanidu…ďe e baraaji."
  2,159,"∆Āen suu…óoo…ďe kon ko Men Jippini immorde e …ďaŇčngannduyee tinndin…óo goona Annabiijo on e kon ko o addi, jeyaa…ďe e Alyahuuda e Annasaara, …ďaawo nde Men Fe√Ī√Īinani …óum yim…ďe …ďen ka defte ma…ď…ďe; …ďen …óon [suu…óoo…ďe], Allah Wo…ó…óintinay-…ďe e Yurmeende Makko, Malaa'ika en e Annabi en e yim…ďe …ďen fof kadi hu…óiray…ďe wo…ó…óintineede e Yumeende Allah."
  2,160,"So wanaa …ďen ruttii…ďe e Allah, nimsu…ďe ko suu…óirani …óeen Aayeeje …ďaŇčngu…óe, …ďe mo∆ī∆īini golleeji ma…ď…ďe fee√Īu…óe e wirnii…óe, …ďe fe√Ī√Īini kon ko …ďe suu…óunoo e goonga e peewal; …ďen …óon, Mi Ja…ďay ruttogol ma…ď…ďe ngol ka …óoftaare Am, tawde ko Miin woni Ja…ďoowo tuubuubuye …ďen tuubay…ďe e jeyaa…ďe …ďen, Yurmetee…óo …ďe."
  2,161,"Pellet, …ďen yeddu…ďe …ďe maayidi e keerefaaku ado …ďe yiltaade e mu'un, ena fawii …ďen …óon kuddi Allah ndin ra…óoreede e Yurmeende Makko nden, ena fawii…ďe kadi kuddi Malaa'ika en e yim…ďe …ďen fof; ra…óoreede e Yurmeende Allah wo…ó…óiŇčtinee e Mu en."
  2,162,"Ko …ďe luttidoo…ďe e ndin kuddi, …ďe hayfinŇčtaake le…ďte …óen hay √Īallal gootal, …ďe nennŇčtaake √Īalnde darngal."
  2,163,"Rewetee…óo mon On e goonga -onon yo yim…ďe- ko O gooto Bajjo ka Jaati Makko e Sifaaji Makko. Rewetee…óo e goona woo alaa tanaa Makko, ko KaŇčko woni Huu…ďu…óo Yurmeende Yaajunde, Heeror…óo Yurmegol jeyaa…ďe Mu'un; sabu O Neemirii…ďe neemaaji …ói limtotaako."